Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:57.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球为什么是圆的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火箭为什么会飞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磁石为什么会相吸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世间的一切事物都能用科学来证明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.30,0:03:17.64,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(480,315)\fs25}墓
