Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:22.91,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}第二堂课  \NTHE  自习
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:26.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头·剪刀·布
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  哇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.26,0:07:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的  麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:42.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才不是说明了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.11,0:07:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢的人要打对方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分哦  好过分的态度哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某种意义上比打我还过分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗？  就像刚才说明的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输的话就防御  赢的话就打人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:56.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}击碎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:07:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是现在啦  为什么现在打呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为我刚才赢了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是现在  那是刚才啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活在当下  活在当下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就是那样的生物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出石头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后出布
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要乱出哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头剪刀布！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就重新来一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头·剪刀·布
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干劲为零啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小丑啊  就像小丑一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神受到打击了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等下  麻衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  你要…干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.24,0:08:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挖到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  这一定是转世再生了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个放这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.17,0:08:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得她很开心的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  那种东西怎样都好  来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  石头·剪刀·布
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻…麻衣  那是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.46,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}决定一击！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是石剪布啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么如此残忍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不算不算  不准出石剪布啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有不准用佛像打人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:01.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}盖斯科因！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  来吧  先出石头…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头·剪刀·布
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是  就是那样哦  麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做还是做得到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:09:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  再来再来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.94,0:10:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  先出石…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOD  IS  DEAD！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:08.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  为什么又要打我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.73,0:10:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  刚才不是玩得很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.50,0:10:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是觉得不想玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以让我看看弥勒菩萨吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:31.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.30,0:00:40.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我去图书馆还书了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好地看家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:54.63,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N21
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.53,0:10:57.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}冰箱上：不可以吃太多冰激凌和果汁哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么名乃的不倒翁只有一只眼睛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  要是博士把眼睛画上去的话  说不定会表扬我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃也许会说「你吃一堆点心也没关系哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.67,0:11:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好像有点画歪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是名乃的  怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  也许会惹她生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时不准博士吃零食！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:48.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  这样画  这样画
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本  怎么办啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:11:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是啥  你这家伙都干了些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是那小姑娘的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它没有眼睛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊  你就照我说的试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先开溜了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  阪本先生你要出门吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要选新借的书所以回来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  你那肚子是怎么回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:55.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿  诶嘿嘿嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:56.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是诶嘿嘿啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.97,0:13:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要生了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  没有那种可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要生了啦！  我要生了  我要生了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:10.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}那个  你这是在玩什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  名乃的弟弟要诞生啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.26,0:13:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.40,0:13:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  姐姐～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.01,0:13:40.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.20,0:00:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:29.95,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,240)\fad(600,0)}钱\N仙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:29.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来玩钱仙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  美绪居然不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.17,0:14:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我稍微说明一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:44.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先在正中画一个鸟居
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后写上「是」与「否」和五十音图  就准备这样的一张纸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:55.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}钱仙又叫狐狗狸，油炸豆腐据说是其喜欢的食物。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然根据地域不同  也有说在纸上写上油炸豆腐会比较好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就按最简单的来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:14:59.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了能让钱仙进来  要打开北边的门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把这枚10円硬币放在这个鸟居的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.42,0:15:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人一起压住硬币  然后问想问的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人的秘密之类的  喜欢的人的事情之类的  苦恼着的事情之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.80,0:15:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话明明什么都没做  10円硬币一下子动了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱仙就会做出回答哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.16,0:15:28.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先不能一个人玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能以开玩笑的心态去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则会被低级灵附身的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  在途中停止的话也会被附身的  要注意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这种感觉  还算是蛮危险的游戏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  总之开始玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.57,0:16:09.22,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,300)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N22
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  今天的课就到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:14.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要进行小考  大家回去要好好学习哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  推迟啦推迟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无论怎么推迟结果都是一样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈  大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱井老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  相生同学  有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些想问的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  是关于前一阵小考的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.67,0:16:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这题是FLY
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我不是问答案
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:44.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}这里指勇者斗恶龙里面的消失咒「ニフラム」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:44.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个看上去好像被下了消失咒的是老师画的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.78,0:16:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得在考试中加入图片能让考试变得更加灵活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:53.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师画的画真有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我不是很擅长画画
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:58.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,题目很难看懂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么老师  下次就用我画的画吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会画得超帅的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说听说我  我画的画会出在小考上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,0:17:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师说了「会用我画的画」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪你现在画的话也许也会出在卷子上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:23.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你说会出  那也有不会出的可能性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧  你不画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我就算了  不必了  我还得去还这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.89,0:17:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  那我就画一个超帅的帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.99,0:17:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这种感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.24,0:17:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的好帅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.68,0:17:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相生同学真会画画呢  佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.99,0:18:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈  其实我就是画得…那么好啦  开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.27,0:18:04.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便说一下画的名字叫做「梅雨下的乔治」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  感觉更加帅了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叫帅！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:17.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  你们两位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般被称作帅的应该是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:23.98,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.61,0:18:23.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个样子的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好厉害  好像漫画一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长野原同学  你有在画漫画吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  嘛  只是稍微画画啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:35.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  下次让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那就有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.71,0:18:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  不可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看  让我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.63,0:18:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  啊  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我画的比你更帅啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:53.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:55.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这不是抄袭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这可不是抄袭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是抄袭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是名为抄袭的致敬！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.79,0:19:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这根本就是承认了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.61,0:19:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都说帅的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.14,0:19:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这样画的话怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:23.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种充满知性的冷酷形象  无论在哪个时代都是女性憧憬的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是眼镜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他视力不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.16,0:19:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是戴上隐形眼镜的话或许更好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙简直完全不懂嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:39.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样画！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.79,0:19:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜戴到耳朵下面了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:44.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  这也是抄袭我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.92,0:19:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧啧  这可是太阳眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.84,0:19:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就没有下限吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这样画呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.53,0:19:53.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从出门迎接到红茶服务
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你大小姐般的享受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受大吉岭红茶的魔力吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  又是眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我不是很懂这方面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼呼呼  不听隐形眼镜的忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃啊！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪你根本就不懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.05,0:20:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥  真正的帅指的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唰唰唰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.37,0:20:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.64,0:20:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮在空中！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等一下  这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车子在开动！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:28.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好像很快  好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你骗谁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.11,0:20:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说帅的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:35.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说帅的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说帅的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.16,0:20:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常识上来说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.02,0:20:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以常识来考虑的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说帅的话！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个样子的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:21:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈  什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:17.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}15:40  1-Q讲台前  长野原美绪  击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:34.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,600)}一句话时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.21,0:21:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边听着爵士乐一边画了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.57,0:21:41.84,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:44.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.54,0:21:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  老湿  早上好！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是老湿啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我现在开始分发早上的小考试卷  请传下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是失败  画画这件事本来我想保密的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.94,0:22:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到居然画出了那样的画
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.29,0:22:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  嘛  尽管我暴走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.07,0:22:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只画到了那种程度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.91,0:22:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算是不幸中之万幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.94,0:22:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能不去想最坏的状况了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.15,0:22:17.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这两三天就得接受祐子的嘲笑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.23,0:22:21.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行  我得振作  继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.01,0:22:27.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪老湿快点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.95,0:22:31.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  考试开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.99,0:22:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪老湿～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.86,0:24:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  咻  啊哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.15,0:24:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  初次见面  我是拟声词
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.44,0:24:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咕噜噜噜噜是不想说的日语呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.82,0:24:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不是什么日语啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.29,0:24:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回的日常是第六话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.04,0:24:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:01.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
